title: The Taj - Alabang
description: Vegetarian Indian grocery store. Carries veggie burgers, veggie ham, wheat gluten, plus typical Indian spices, grains, chickpeas, lentils, breads, etc. Most items are vegan suitable, a few with dairy. Read the labels.
streetAddress: Unit 108 &109, One Legacy Place, Don Jesus Blvd, Muntinlupa City
